[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1045","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1045.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1329","title":"Red Hat Linux SysVInit 缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.1 及更早版本中的 SysVInit 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过向 SysVInit 发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 5.1 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。由于攻击者需要本地访问权限，攻击门槛较高，但一旦利用成功可完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1329"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:12.473","remediation":"升级至 Red Hat Linux 5.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 SysVInit 缓冲区溢出问题。对于已停止支持的旧版本，建议迁移至现代受支持的 RHEL 发行版（如 RHEL 7/8/9），并确保系统初始化组件保持最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7250.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#SysVinit","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1329.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1329","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1329.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1329.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vcmw-4q9q-gx59/GHSA-vcmw-4q9q-gx59.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83032/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1329.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ad7c142ce47bdca962dc5352eae3764ce44639d2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1045.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1042","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1042.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1327","title":"Red Hat Linux linuxconf 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linuxconf 1.11r11-rh2 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，该漏洞存在于 Red Hat Linux 5.1 系统中。本地攻击者可通过向 LANG 环境变量提交超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用此漏洞可获取系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响范围有限，但危害严重，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限才能利用。建议升级到不受影响的版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1327"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:12.240","remediation":"升级 linuxconf 至 1.11r12 及以上版本，或升级 Red Hat Linux 至 6.0 以上版本。如无法升级，可限制本地用户设置 LANG 环境变量的权限，或移除 linuxconf 的 SUID 位作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221103125826&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7239.php","http://www.osvdb.org/6065","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh51-errata-general.html#linuxconf","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1327.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1327","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1327.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1327.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7q8-jmgx-5r5x/GHSA-m7q8-jmgx-5r5x.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1327.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001025.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b115a892-9703-4890-943d-0adee51a249b.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1042.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1041","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1041.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1325","title":"SAS System 5.18 for VAX/VMS 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SAS System 5.18 for VAX/VMS 存在不安全的目录和启动文件权限配置漏洞。由于系统安装时未正确设置目录及启动文件的访问权限，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞修改或替换关键文件，从而获取更高权限。该漏洞影响 SAS System 5.18 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户升级至修复版本或手动调整文件权限配置。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1325"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.993","remediation":"立即修复 SAS System 5.18 安装目录及启动文件的权限配置，确保目录权限设置为 755（drwxr-xr-x），启动文件权限设置为 644（-rw-r--r--），仅允许管理员（SYSTEM/ROOT）拥有写入权限。同时移除不必要的世界可写（world-writable）权限位，并定期审计文件权限变更。如条件允许，升级到 SAS System 6.0 及以上版本以彻底解决权限问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/c-19.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7261","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1325.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1325","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1325.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1325.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jm5h-qhv5-56m7/GHSA-jm5h-qhv5-56m7.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1325.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001024.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b9213ca3-14e3-4d16-a7ae-ead8dd18b297.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1041.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1039","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1039.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1320","title":"Novell NetWare 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 3.x 及早期版本存在本地权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过伪造数据包（packet spoofing）方式利用该漏洞，获取目标系统更高权限。该漏洞影响 Novell NetWare 3.x 及更早版本，攻击者需具备本地访问权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议用户升级至不受影响的版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1320"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.360","remediation":"升级至 NetWare 4.x 或更高版本，该版本引入 NCP 分组签名机制。如在 3.x 环境无法升级，可在 AUTOEXEC.NCF 中设置 `SET NCP PACKET SIGNATURE OPTION = 3`，强制要求所有 NCP 请求进行数字签名，防止伪造 NCP 分组实施权限提升。同时建议在交换机上启用端口安全（Port Security）和 DHCP Snooping，限制局域网内的 ARP 欺骗与分组注入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/d-01.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7213.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1320.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1320","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1320.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1320.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rc2p-chmj-rg4f/GHSA-rc2p-chmj-rg4f.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1320.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001022.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ca5ab8a6-abe1-44eb-bf87-3f756f26a751.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1039.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1038","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1038.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1317","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 SP4 及更早版本存在本地权限提升漏洞。本地用户可通过在 \\?? 对象文件夹中使用不同大小写字母修改符号链接表，将链接指向不同的设备对象，从而获取更高系统权限。该漏洞需攻击者拥有本地访问权限，影响范围包括 Windows NT 4.0 全系版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。由于相关系统已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1317"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"