//github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1038.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1037","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1037.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1316","title":"Microsoft Windows NT SP2 密码安全筛选策略漏洞","description":"Windows NT SP2 附带的 Passfilt.dll 密码过滤器存在设计缺陷，无法有效阻止用户设置包含用户名的密码。攻击者可利用该漏洞，通过结合已知用户名进行针对性密码猜测攻击，大幅降低暴力破解难度，可能导致未授权访问或权限提升。该漏洞影响 Windows NT SP2 系统，需用户交互触发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1316"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:10.843","remediation":"Windows NT 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2019/2022 或更高版本。若无法升级，在 Windows NT 中可通过「域安全策略」→「密码策略」启用「密码必须符合复杂性要求」，并禁用允许密码包含用户名的策略，同时设置密码长度最小值≥8 位。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q247/9/75.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7391","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1316.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1316","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1316.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1316.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m9pv-rhw7-3fh9/GHSA-m9pv-rhw7-3fh9.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1316.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001020.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962