0a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1315.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1036.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1035","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1035.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1307","title":"Novell UnixWare urestore 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell UnixWare 1.1 系统中的 urestore 恢复工具存在权限许可漏洞，本地普通用户可利用该程序在处理文件恢复操作时未正确验证权限的缺陷，通过精心构造的恢复请求绕过系统权限检查，从而获取 root 超级用户权限。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，无需身份认证即可利用，成功利用后可完全控制目标系统，造成机密性、完整性和可用性全面丧失。该漏洞影响 Novell UnixWare 1.1 版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1307"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:09.703","remediation":"建议升级到 Novell UnixWare 2.0 或更高版本。如无法升级，可立即移除 `/bin/urestore` 的 setuid 权限：`chmod u-s /bin/urestore`。同时限制本地用户登录权限，仅允许受信任的管理员通过 su/sudo 执行特权操作，并在系统层面启用文件访问审计 (audit) 以监控异常提权行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/f-06.shtml","http://www.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1994_4/0676.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1307.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1307","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1307.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1307.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cr84-5qj8-f776/GHSA-cr84-5qj8-f776.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1307.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fca28a80-1505-4ad5-962e-45d3a10f89e6.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1035.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1034","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1034.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1300","title":"Cray UNICOS accton 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Cray UNICOS 6.1 及 6.0 版本中的 accton 命令存在任意文件读取漏洞。由于程序未对文件路径和访问权限进行充分校验，本地攻击者可通过传入特制参数或利用符号链接攻击的方式，以 accton 进程权限读取系统任意文件内容，同时可修改系统审计（accounting）配置，导致敏感信息泄露及审计日志异常。该漏洞需要本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 3.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1300"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:08.807","remediation":"升级 Cray UNICOS 至 6.1 以上版本，或应用厂商针对 accton 的专用补丁。限制 accton 可执行文件的访问权限为仅 root 用户可执行（chmod 700 /usr/sbin/accton），并移除普通用户的 setuid 权限。同时通过文件系统 ACL 限制 /var/adm/pacct 等记账文件的读取权限，仅授权审计员可访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/b-31.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1300.json","http