序，改为直接运行，并收紧用户目录的 ACL 访问控制列表权限。作为临时缓解措施，可禁用 Office 快捷工具栏启动程序的功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q146/6/04.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/562","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1294.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1294","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1294.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1294.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2g26-89g9-8v94/GHSA-2g26-89g9-8v94.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87847/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1294.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1033.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1032","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1032.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1290","title":"nftp FTP客户端 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"nftp FTP 客户端 1.40 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程恶意 FTP 服务器可通过向客户端发送超长的响应字符串触发该漏洞，导致客户端拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意代码。攻击者只需搭建恶意 FTP 服务器并诱导目标用户连接即可实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1290"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:07.313","remediation":"请立即停止使用 nftp 1.40 及更早版本，升级至后继项目 tnftp（Debian 系统中安装 tnftp 包 ≥ 20200705 版本，其他系统可安装 NetBSD tnftp ≥ 20210827）。该漏洞已在 tnftp 的后续重写中得到修复。若无法升级，可改用 curl 或 lftp 等更成熟的 FTP 客户端替代，并在防火墙或应用层面仅允许连接可信任的 FTP 服务器作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91127951426494&w=2","http://www.ayukov.com/nftp/history.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1397","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1290.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1290","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1290.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1290.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g5wr-v48w-5f62/GHSA-g5wr-v48w-5f62.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87793/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1290.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1032.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1031","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1031.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1287","title":"Analog 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Analog 统计分析软件 3.0 及更早版本中存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 forms 接口向目标系统发送特制请求，利用路径遍历或未授权访问方式读取服务器上的任意文件，包括配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Analog 3.0 及之前所有版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议用户升级至最新版本或限制 forms 接口的访问权限以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1287"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.927","remediation":"升级 Analog 至 3.1 或更高版本，该版本对 forms 接口输入进行了路径验证，防止目录遍历攻击。如继续使用 CGI 模式，建议在 Web 服务器层面限制对 forms 接口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 提交查询。Analog 项目已于 2004 年停止维护，建议迁移至 GoAccess 或 Matomo 等现代日志分析工具。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.statslab.cam.ac.uk/~sret1/analog/security.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1410","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1287","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1287.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f974-p775-h8x3/GHSA-f974-p775-h8x3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87844/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1031.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1031.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1030","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1030.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1279","title":"IBM AS/400 与 Microsoft SNA Server 共享文件夹信息泄露漏洞","description":"AS/400 共享文件夹功能与 Microsoft SNA Server 3.0 及更早版本的交互存在信息泄露漏洞。当多个用户共享同一个本地 APPC 逻辑单元（LU）时，由于会话隔离机制不完善，用户可越权查看彼此共享文件夹内容。该漏洞无需特殊权限，攻击者只需与目标共享同一 Local APPC LU 即可触发，导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1279"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:05.937","remediation":"升级 Microsoft SNA Server 至 4.0 或更高版本以修复该交互问题；在 AS/400 端为每个用户分配独立的 Local APPC LU，避免共享同一 LU 导致文件夹互访；如无需共享文件夹功能，可在 AS/400 上禁用该特性作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q138/0/01.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1548","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1279","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1279.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3qcq-w2m6-vwwx/GHSA-3qcq-w2m6-vwwx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87845/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001013.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1030.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1026","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1259","title":"Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh Edition 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh 版在创建文件时未能正确初始化所分配的磁盘空间，导致已删除文件的数据残留被嵌入新生成的 Office 文件中，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者可通过获取目标用户共享的 Office 文件，从中提取可能包含密码、文档内容等敏感数据的残留信息。该漏洞影响 Office 98 Macintosh Edition，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，利用条件较为受限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1259"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.430","remediation":"无法获取准确补丁信息（KB189529 链接已失效），但该漏洞仅影响 Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh Edition。建议升级到 Office 2001 for Mac 或更高版本，新版 Office 在文件创建时正确初始化磁盘空间，不会泄露已删除文件数据。如暂时无法升级，可在创建敏感 Office 文件前使用安全删除工具彻底擦除磁盘空闲空间。目前 Office 98 已停止支持，升级是唯一根治措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q189/5/29.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1780","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1259","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1259.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4fg5-9xqq-h6cq/GHSA-4fg5-9xqq-h6cq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87853/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_infor.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1012","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1223","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10794,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10813}}","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 在处理 ASP 页面请求时存在拒绝服务漏洞。其 URL 解析逻辑未能对路径中的正斜杠（/）字符数量进行合理限制，当远程攻击者向目标服务器发送一个 URL 中包含大量连续斜杠的特制 ASP 页面请求时，服务器会因异常的资源消耗或解析异常而无法正常响应后续请求，导致服务中断。该漏洞影响运行 Microsoft IIS 3.0 且启用 ASP 功能的 Web 服务器，攻击者无需身份认证，只需能通过网络访问目标站点即可发起攻击，利用方式简单，可对站点可用性造成严重影响。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1223"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:58.883","remediation":"建议将 Microsoft IIS 3.0 升级至 IIS 4.0 或更高版本（如 Windows 2000 自带的 IIS 5.0），从根本上修复 ASP 页面解析缺陷。若暂无法升级，可在 IIS 中限制单个请求 URL 长度、配置 URLScan 工具过滤含异常数量斜杠的请求，并部署前端防火墙/反向代理限制超大 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施，同时监控 ASP 站点异常访问日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q187/5/03.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3892","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1223.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1223.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1223","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3d905f6009ce1a0cb55b6b90198454d955586615/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1223.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1223.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cj4j-jmwc-f6jm/GHSA-cj4j-jmwc-f6jm.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87550/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1223.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1012.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1012.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1012.toml"}]